<p>The <code>until</code> tag loops until a condition becomes true.</p>

<h2>Basic Until Loop</h2>
<pre>{open}set $i = 1{close}
{open}until $i gt 5{close}
  Item {open}$i{close}
  {open}increment $i{close}
{open}/until{close}</pre>
{set $i = 1}
<ul>
{until $i gt 5}
  <li>Item {$i}</li>
  {increment $i}
{/until}
</ul>

<h2>Until vs While Comparison</h2>
<p><b>while $i le 5</b> = loop while i &lt;= 5 (same as <b>until $i gt 5</b>)</p>

<h2>Until with Counter</h2>
<pre>{open}set $n = 0{close}
{open}until $n eq 10{close}
  {open}$n{close}
  {open}set $n = $n + 2{close}
{open}/until{close}</pre>
{set $n = 0}
<p>Even numbers:
{until $n eq 10}
{$n}
{set $n = $n + 2}
{/until}
</p>
